career_objectives.value:
Senior web developer specializing in Drupal content management framework. Proven ability to adapt in both self-starting and collaborative environments while staying focused on achieving high-quality results under strict deadlines. While working as a web developer for over 10 years, I am always learning more, and have a passion for keeping up to date with current technology and programming languages. Over 8 years experience working with Drupal 8, and just over 3 years working with Drupal 9, I have recently been acclimating myself with Drupal 10. 

As a senior web developer, I rely on my vast set of skills to achieve successful completion of tasks over a wide range of needs.
